{"tid":1547212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[黑警殺人之謎] 近排有多咗人自殺? 關八三一事?","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T16:13:21.000Z","uid":29218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01a2b0d14a85f5d43602aa73226f591bd8774388","tid":1547212,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=47f7040c\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<br />\n香港每日都有好多人自殺<br />\n我唔知黑警有無殺人 有無非法處理屍體<br />\n但我從自殺個案數量來看<br />\n過去幾日自殺人數無特別高<br />\n就算八三一真有死人 估計屍體當作自殺個案機會不大<br />\n因為風險頗高"},{"pid":"a53a8f77f7600fcbe3ae03539001c397215ad3bf","tid":1547212,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85f8f5baaa366965d3e4838384c71b91994f7b80","tid":1547212,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"資料作者：Benny Yeong<br />\n<a href=\"https://tvmost.com.hk/201904221901_video_wedreport_suicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftvmost.com.hk%2F201904221901_video_wedreport_suicide&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b3ffa98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tvmost.com.hk/201904221901_video_wedreport_suicide</a>"},{"pid":"006a03292e9fe0cb2